Create a UserSurveyForm component that gathers feedback from users.

The layout should be:

A Text header: "User Feedback Survey"

A RadioButton group asking "How satisfied are you?" with options: "Very Satisfied", "Satisfied", "Neutral", "Dissatisfied", and "Very Dissatisfied"

A TextArea for additional comments, only shown if the selected satisfaction level is not "Very Satisfied"

A Toggle labeled "Would you like to be contacted for follow-up?"

If the toggle is enabled, show an Input field for the user's email

A Button at the bottom labeled "Submit Feedback"

On submission, show a Toast with the message "Thank you for your feedback!"

Variables:

"satisfaction" (string)

"comments" (string)

"followUp" (boolean)

"email" (string)

"showToast" (boolean)